lead_paragraph: Toppling forward, Henrikh Mkhitaryan looked like he'd misjudged the right-wing cross as he surged into the box seeking a clinching goal for Manchester United.

headline.print_headline: Mkhitaryan Masterpiece Keeps Man United Rolling in EPL
